metadata.name: Spoiled Young Ape Club 0001
metadata.description: Inspired by the TV show "Growing Pains", our apes are just like the Seaver - experiencing growing pains and looking to cause trouble. These 5,555 unique young apes are looking for ways to entertain themselves by getting up to mischief. SYAC is an NFT collection consisting of young apes with over 200 accessories, expressions and clothing generated by an algorithm. Our NFT Collection offers high utilities to our members in a sustainable way with IRL bitcoin mining and each NFT holder will earn 10 tokens by holding our NFTs per day. This means that you can enjoy earning a passive income whilst holding our NFTs.
